verses.rendering:
Heshbon and Elealeh cry out;
their voice is heard as far as Jahaz.
Therefore the soldiers of Moab tremble;
their courage fails them.

For the waters of Nimrim are desolate;
the grass is withered, the vegetation is gone,
nothing green remains.

For the cry of anguish encircles the borders of Moab;
her wailing reaches Eglaim;
her wailing reaches Beer-elim.
